title: Jin Di Lu’s Website
text:
Hello, I’m Jin Di, but you can just call me Jin.
I’m currently a student at the University of Toronto’s iSchool studying Information Sciences with a focus in UX and Data Sciences. I’m still figuring out which direction I want to head into.
If you want to contact me, you can email me at: chrislu2234@gmail.com
